title: Eileen Myles Offers A Double Shot Of Punk Rock Poetry
text: Eileen Myles Offers A Double Shot Of Punk Rock Poetry Sunday, 25 October 2015 (11 minutes ago) The veteran poet's beloved 1994 novel Chelsea Girls has been reissued alongside a new collection, I Must Be Living Twice. Myles' poems chronicle a life of art and sex in gritty 1970s New York City .
